    <text id="A8056T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Speck seeks to collect debt from McCue.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <abbr expan="David">D.</abbr> Speck<lb/><hi rend="underline">1860</hi>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1859-11-03">Nov. 3<hi rend="underline">rd</hi> 1859</date>
                        <name type="place">Arbor Hill</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>To: <abbr expan="John">Jno.</abbr> H. McCue<lb/>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I wish you would send me ten Dollars. It being the remainder of what you owe me.
                    i am very much in need of money now. I am informed you are doing very well in
                    Nelson <abbr expan="County">Co.</abbr> which i am glad to hear. <orig
                        reg="write">wright</orig> me on <orig reg="receipt">recipt</orig> of this.
                    let me know if you are flush. Send the ten along</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>yours. Respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>David Speck</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">I will Recpt. <abbr expan="David Speck">D.
                    S.</abbr></seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
